Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.37,0:00:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,早安 我是筧純
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,終於到了暖洋洋的冬季了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.04,0:00:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 大家也注意到了\N這個巨乳了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.92,0:00:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道啊 男人都是會色瞇瞇\N盯著女人的胸部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.89,0:00:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,跳動抖動 我也知道你們\N注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,對這種巨乳 到底會幻想\N什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.13,0:01:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,（不戴胸罩的透明巨乳）\N（J罩杯小姐姐 筧純）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.19,0:01:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？等一下\N怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧 壞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這個怎麼辦\N是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這個怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真是抱歉\N沒有關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好熱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好軟是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好軟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼様
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,濕了 抱歉\N這邊也要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 濕漉漉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好色情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,濕漉漉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,直接摸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可以是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼粗了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,想摸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.54,0:17:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,胸部這麼大 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊的乳頭也想試試
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.58,0:22:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.29,0:22:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了 高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.90,0:22:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.93,0:25:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.13,0:27:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,看看可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.42,0:29:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股給我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.07,0:31:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.01,0:31:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.91,0:31:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊\N高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.12,0:32:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.93,0:32:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好激烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.37,0:33:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.78,0:33:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我是預約了的山田\N麻煩您安排一下
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.28,0:33:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 我確認一下 稍等一下\N好的 麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.26,0:33:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是櫃台
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.56,0:33:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,預約的山田先生到了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.90,0:34:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 明白 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.80,0:34:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,到會議室等一下可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.71,0:34:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,會議室啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.04,0:34:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩您稍等一下\N不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.31,0:34:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,右邊那裡是電梯
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.72,0:34:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在四樓裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.79,0:34:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係吧\N是的 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.89,0:34:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,再確認一下\N抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.23,0:34:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,右邊有電梯 在四樓
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.57,0:34:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.84,0:34:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.77,0:34:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 明白了\N知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.61,0:34:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可以到會議室坐一下\N可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.88,0:34:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.08,0:34:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思\N我帶您過去
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.72,0:34:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.33,0:35:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.31,0:35:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.42,0:35:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 胸部這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.02,0:35:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好喜歡\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.13,0:35:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要著急
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.13,0:35:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 就一點點 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.97,0:35:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,小聲一點 馬上就結束
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.97,0:35:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,求妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.28,0:35:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 真的 這個可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.12,0:35:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.12,0:36:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有關係的 好喜歡 喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.42,0:36:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好興奮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.56,0:36:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真是漂亮 好軟\N好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.37,0:36:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣 從來沒有試過
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.51,0:36:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,能否負責啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.35,0:36:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.86,0:36:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,摸一下
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.50,0:36:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣了 好興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.81,0:36:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好粗了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.34,0:37:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了 這麼可愛的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.61,0:37:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,胸部這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.75,0:37:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好興奮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.69,0:37:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,摸一下 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.29,0:37:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,求妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.77,0:37:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,摸一下
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.19,0:37:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.37,0:37:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.14,0:38:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.91,0:38:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,雙手摸一下可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.72,0:38:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.69,0:38:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的感覺是吧\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.50,0:38:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣 好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.74,0:38:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續 激烈一點 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.25,0:38:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣是吧\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.65,0:38:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊的蛋蛋也要\N好的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.36,0:39:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.17,0:39:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣 激烈一點可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.24,0:39:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,用嘴舔一下可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.15,0:39:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,求妳了 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.92,0:39:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了 舌頭好軟
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.07,0:40:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,啪啦啪啦舔龜頭可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.19,0:40:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,用肉棒抵住胸部\N可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.48,0:40:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.06,0:41:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太棒了 滑溜溜的\N真是舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.66,0:41:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺到了 這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.93,0:41:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,摸一下可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.18,0:41:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太棒了 胸部好軟
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.74,0:41:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,抵住乳頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.59,0:42:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.19,0:42:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續摸一下
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.04,0:42:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 好興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.82,0:42:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,真是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.91,0:43:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.55,0:43:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒好硬了 沒有關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.56,0:43:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.60,0:43:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.17,0:43:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不行啊 要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.01,0:43:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好軟 夾住可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.08,0:43:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害\N真的好軟
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.85,0:43:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.73,0:43:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜歡是吧\N不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.90,0:44:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.10,0:44:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,和多少根肉棒做過這個
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.91,0:44:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 動起來 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.92,0:44:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,摩擦著好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.54,0:44:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.88,0:44:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.29,0:45:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.59,0:45:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這個事情請你保密
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.26,0:45:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.78,0:45:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有請下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.28,0:45:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.06,0:46:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.89,0:46:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是怎麼了\N昨天開始有點疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.43,0:46:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,然後 沒有什麼食慾\N這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.47,0:46:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,喉嚨有點疼\N這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.54,0:46:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.55,0:46:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有測了提問嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.25,0:46:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,測過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.65,0:46:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是沒有發燒吧\N這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.33,0:46:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那麽 生活方面\N生活沒問題 可能冷著了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.53,0:46:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,冷著啊\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.11,0:46:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,醫生？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.78,0:46:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.11,0:47:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有發燒是吧\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.98,0:47:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 沒有發燒就沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.09,0:47:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.16,0:47:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 我們簡單檢查一下\N您先把包包放好 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.70,0:47:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,後面轉過來\N好的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.51,0:47:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,衣服撩起來 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.82,0:47:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 我確認一下哦\N好的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.05,0:48:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.70,0:48:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 轉過來正面可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.91,0:48:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.94,0:48:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,撩起來可以吧\N不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.54,0:49:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,深呼吸一下\N好的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.71,0:49:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.14,0:49:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 聽到沒問題
